</style><p>至于尼吉三吉的印尼人才，据透露，2023年将有多名印尼人才陆续毕业，看来该计划正成为虚拟的“毕业多米诺骨牌”。</p><p> 4月10日，有四个人： <strong>ZEA Cornelia</strong> 、Taka <strong>Radjiman</strong> 、Siska <strong>Leontyne</strong>和<strong>Amicia</strong> Michela。 6月30日，宣布四名学生毕业：Azura <strong>Cecillia</strong> 、Nara <strong>Haramaung</strong> 、 <strong>Reza</strong> <strong>Avanluna、</strong> Hyona Elatiora。最近宣布Shea Ekafila、Mika Meratika、Rixa Dhirendra毕业，共10人（不含Rixa Dhirendra）将于 2023 年离开 Nijisanji。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="dYI249DPvs"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/4-vtubers-formerly-affiliated-to-nijisanji-id-will-graduate-sequentially-after-may/">从5月起，来自Nijisanji和NIJISANJI ID的四位VTuber将一一毕业。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“属于 Nijisanji 和 NIJISANJI ID 的四位 VTuber 将从 5 月起逐步毕业” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/4-vtubers-formerly-affiliated-to-nijisanji-id-will-graduate-sequentially-after-may/embed/#?secret=wY4PU8zzXj#?secret=dYI249DPvs" data-secret="dYI249DPvs" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="Ezx4jkVLQ2"><a href="https://p2y.jp/4-more-former-nijisanji-id-vtuber-to-graduate/">属于Nijisanji和Nijisanji ID的另外四位VTuber将陆续毕业</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Nijisanji 和 NIJISANJI ID 的另外 4 名 VTuber 将按顺序毕业” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/4-more-former-nijisanji-id-vtuber-to-graduate/embed/#?secret=ZFNwhp8VBN#?secret=Ezx4jkVLQ2" data-secret="Ezx4jkVLQ2" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><p></p><