display: block;
}
}
</style><p>目前，由于成员之间的纠纷，东海On Air正处于“火焰”之中，UUUM于10月19日<em>发表声明称，“在SNS上发布了存在合规问题的评论和视频。</em> <em>”对于我们创作者的行为给许多人带来的不适，我们深表歉意</em>。”</p><blockquote class="wp-block-quote"><p> <a href="https://www.uuum.co.jp/news/109573" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="关于我们的创作者的道歉和报告">关于我们的创作者的道歉和报告</a></p><cite>乌鲁木齐大学</cite></blockquote><p>最近删除 Gweru 先生的帖子（推文）被认为是对 Tokai On Air 目前遇到问题这一事实的回应。 </p><p></p><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="EFst8iJCBP"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-vtuber-gwelu-os-gar-announces-publication-of-apology-video-and-suspension-of-activities/">Nijisanji所属VTuber Gwel Osu Girl发布道歉视频并宣布暂停活动</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Nijisanji所属VTuber Gwel Osu Girl发布道歉视频并宣布暂停活动” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/nijisanji-vtuber-gwelu-os-gar-announces-publication-of-apology-video-and-suspension-of-activities/embed/#?secret=A3ZXVZbtSS#?secret=EFst8iJCBP" data-secret="EFst8iJCBP" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="aEUtpiu36K"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/slander-damage-to-vtuber-gwel-os-girl-and-others/">Pekora Usada演唱歌曲的视频发布后，VTuber Gweru Osu Girl等人遭受诽谤。</a> </blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="“Pekora Usada演唱主题曲的视频发布后，VTuber Gweru Osu Girl等遭受诽谤” — P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/slander-damage-to-vtuber-gwel-os-girl-and-others/embed/#?secret=9MsF0SqBIo#?secret=aEUtpiu36K" data-secret="aEUtpiu36K" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><blockquote class="wp-block-quote